niagara.optimizer.colombia
Class MExpr

java.lang.Object
  niagara.optimizer.colombia.MExpr

public class MExpr
extends java.lang.Object

MULTI_EXPRESSIONS MExpr is a compact form of Expr which utilizes sharing. Inputs are GROUPs instead of EXPRs, so the MExpr embodies several EXPRs. All searching is done with M_EXPRs, so each contains lots of state.
